import sys
from datetime import datetime as dt

dformat = "%a %d %b %Y %H:%M:%S %z"
def time_delta(t1, t2):
    first = dt.strptime(t1, dformat) 
    second = dt.strptime(t2, dformat) 
    
    return int(abs((first - second).total_seconds()))
